{"tid":380984,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[自駕遊] 8日台中行程問題同求建議","createTime":"2017-08-30T14:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T03:39:16.000Z","uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6079bfd67277e0cc9c1ab53a3706c5e74d73d3cf","tid":380984,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T14:16:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的,小弟同兩個朋友10月頭會去台中<br />\n上網做過下功課,依家大概定個行程就咁:<br />\nDay 1,2 台中<br />\nDay 3 清境-合歡山 (清境民宿)<br />\nDay 4 日月潭-集集 (集集民宿?<br />\nDay 5 忘憂森林-妖怪村 (玩唔玩到一日?<br />\nDay 6 阿里山-奮起湖 (阿里山民宿)<br />\nDay 7,8 台中<br />\n以上行程有無咩大問題?<br />\n台中市市區有咩好去處,仲有無咩地點係巴絲推薦去?<br />\n同埋租車嗰度有無咩注意?因為中間幾日都係行山路多,唔知有無咩特別要留意<br />\n唔該咁多巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec3eb10105e51e7a6f23335f2fbb567593a716c","tid":380984,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T14:25:54.000Z","msg":"有無興趣浸温泉同玩煙花，有個話去完清境可以去盧山，有條捷徑由清境去盧山只是９個字"},{"pid":"50db4ef88a1bf0ed8b1f85aa2b902e5cd0c98ecd","tid":380984,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無興趣浸温泉同玩煙花，有個話去完清境可以去盧山，有條捷徑由清境去盧山只是９個字</blockquote><br />\n煙火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但10月會唔會仲係好熱?浸溫泉會唔會不智?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1624633d33b39bdde147c9b5ea5ab594583ed688","tid":380984,"uid":13450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:00:00.000Z","msg":"忘憂係大伏"},{"pid":"ac1c313109381a9a6905074265e6d16a11b436af","tid":380984,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:07:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無興趣浸温泉同玩煙花，有個話去完清境可以去盧山，有條捷徑由清境去盧山只是９個字</blockquote><br />\n煙火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但10月會唔會仲係好熱?浸溫泉會唔會不智?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇溜１０月頭，當我無講過"},{"pid":"8f65e729549f8c1f36f9f706867db09eaecf1f3f","tid":380984,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/230918_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F230918_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=54b95c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/230951_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F230951_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=78a3499f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去清境可以夜晚去跟團去觀星，我覺得勁青春咁玩"},{"pid":"7c5ef93e5a9d092dda7bd0bdfbb9f629aa74bc9c","tid":380984,"uid":124438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的,小弟同兩個朋友10月頭會去台中<br />\n上網做過下功課,依家大概定個行程就咁:<br />\nDay 1,2 台中<br />\nDay 3 清境-合歡山 (清境民宿)<br />\nDay 4 日月潭-集集 (集集民宿?<br />\nDay 5 忘憂森林-妖怪村 (玩唔玩到一日?<br />\nDay 6 阿里山-奮起湖 (阿里山民宿)<br />\nDay 7,8 台中<br />\n以上行程有無咩大問題?<br />\n台中市市區有咩好去處,仲有無咩地點係巴絲推薦去?<br />\n同埋租車嗰度有無咩注意?因為中間幾日都係行山路多,唔知有無咩特別要留意<br />\n唔該咁多巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十月中去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行程同你差唔多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1 早機攞車直上清境<br />\nDay 2 清境 &gt; 合歡山 &gt; 日月潭<br />\nDay 3 日月潭<br />\nDay 4 日月潭 &gt; 天空之橋 &gt; 阿里山<br />\nDay 5 阿里山 &gt; 台中<br />\nDay 6 7 台中<br />\nDay 8 早機返香港<br />\n<br />\n頭五日都係自駕<br />\n台中其中一日想去高美濕地，但又唔想租多日車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下台中市入去通常要幾耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7d6fcfa3f21f4695af78239c76ee764d218fae","tid":380984,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:46:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>忘憂係大伏</blockquote><br />\n唔撚係掛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點伏法?<br />\n咁妖怪村點睇?"},{"pid":"6bb794a4b4a4f817861c08358958636c7b93125d","tid":380984,"uid":66027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:49:06.000Z","msg":"唔去高美濕地？"},{"pid":"bcd5840371d40f990c7006d1fa5872bfae3b747d","tid":380984,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔去高美濕地？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打仲有咩推介?<br />\n台中有成4日時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709e150049ef353fb978d9bc1c30a2b8603aa784","tid":380984,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T15:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>是咁的,小弟同兩個朋友10月頭會去台中<br />\n上網做過下功課,依家大概定個行程就咁:<br />\nDay 1,2 台中<br />\nDay 3 清境-合歡山 (清境民宿)<br />\nDay 4 日月潭-集集 (集集民宿?<br />\nDay 5 忘憂森林-妖怪村 (玩唔玩到一日?<br />\nDay 6 阿里山-奮起湖 (阿里山民宿)<br />\nDay 7,8 台中<br />\n以上行程有無咩大問題?<br />\n台中市市區有咩好去處,仲有無咩地點係巴絲推薦去?<br />\n同埋租車嗰度有無咩注意?因為中間幾日都係行山路多,唔知有無咩特別要留意<br />\n唔該咁多巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十月中去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行程同你差唔多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1 早機攞車直上清境<br />\nDay 2 清境 &gt; 合歡山 &gt; 日月潭<br />\nDay 3 日月潭<br />\nDay 4 日月潭 &gt; 天空之橋 &gt; 阿里山<br />\nDay 5 阿里山 &gt; 台中<br />\nDay 6 7 台中<br />\nDay 8 早機返香港<br />\n<br />\n頭五日都係自駕<br />\n台中其中一日想去高美濕地，但又唔想租多日車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下台中市入去通常要幾耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日月潭可以玩到成日?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f560e773370cf702a84f2baa5ac8b678dd4e62a","tid":380984,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T19:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae60241aeb6e7759cfdae5319d156f6d37f22469","tid":380984,"uid":24682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T19:16:42.000Z","msg":"揸車記得盡量靠左<br />\n右邊好多電單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台中電單車算有規律全部靠右行<br />\n其他地方d人成日左穿右插<br />\n要小心d<br />\n最好搵個fd幫你係右邊睇位<br />\n<br />\n路邊停車開門睇清楚無電單車先好開<br />\n祝你旅途愉快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01cf38f7620345113eeb818a7ac40ae37a0b3999","tid":380984,"uid":24682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T19:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸車記得盡量靠左<br />\n右邊好多電單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台中電單車算有規律全部靠右行<br />\n其他地方d人成日左穿右插<br />\n要小心d<br />\n最好搵個fd幫你係右邊睇位<br />\n<br />\n路邊停車開門睇清楚無電單車先好開<br />\n祝你旅途愉快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBtw 同上邊位巴打一樣，想提你日月潭好撚悶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實玩半日都已經玩哂"},{"pid":"3c6cdf63cd62c2fd35b5ec324711880d989168c4","tid":380984,"uid":24682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T19:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>揸車記得盡量靠左<br />\n右邊好多電單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台中電單車算有規律全部靠右行<br />\n其他地方d人成日左穿右插<br />\n要小心d<br />\n最好搵個fd幫你係右邊睇位<br />\n<br />\n路邊停車開門睇清楚無電單車先好開<br />\n祝你旅途愉快<i