":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:02:30.000Z","msg":"自駕過台灣好多次<br />\n<br />\n台中清境就三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n忘憂係伏<br />\n<br />\n台中既景點好散，每個景點要花好多時間去，但逗留時間唔多，除左清景呢d大點，逗留一個鐘都俾多<br />\n<br />\n集集唔駛留咁耐，好撚多大陸人，一粒鐘睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建議去車埕，好靚<br />\n<br />\n新社古堡都唔錯，新社好多姑類手信<br />\n<br />\n高美濕地一定要去，租多日車都值得去，好靚，搭車超煩（除非的士）<br />\n<br />\n得閒冇野做可以揸去家樂福行街，買一兩百就有免費泊車<br />\n<br />\n可以睇下汽車旅館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平靚正<br />\n<br />\n妖怪村冇想像中咁正，辛苦揸上去，一粒鐘行完<br />\n<br />\n揸車小心綿羊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別係綠燈開車果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋轉右果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔建議自駕上合歡山睇日出，因為天未光黑麻麻，冇燈，單程路，又眼訓又凍，俾少少錢（有巴士/包車3000twd),佢地熟路好安全，睇完日出又要揸返落黎，攞苦黎辛，訓多覺好過"},{"pid":"ed27685feb04cfb62c5d69a410c1e62b5d48851c","tid":380984,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"租車首推艾租士focus1.5<br />\n<br />\n實冇後悔<br />\n<br />\n四人連行李都闊落，易睇位"},{"pid":"07ebb914b460fb86c1fcff60dcac0e152431c50a","tid":380984,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:04:10.000Z","msg":"落雨小心，幾個月前雨季去左，好狼狽，一個月後新聞話塌路，封埋山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 斷晒來往咁滯"},{"pid":"7feb9c4f5e146c689d2c30ceb757140938be7507","tid":380984,"uid":119017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T18:06:25.000Z","msg":"月底去，唔識揸車，問左d包車司機 6000 台幣一日，請問是咪正常價？<br />\n<br />\n打算day 1 上清境住一晚去埋合歡山睇日出，day 2下午出返台中市，去逢甲夜市，day 3 想join 個day tour順便去高美濕地，day 4去921 地震博物館之後返香港。"},{"pid":"655cab5cfed7e2db3015f110bb01defe6c1926e4","tid":380984,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T21:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>是咁的,小弟同兩個朋友10月頭會去台中<br />\n上網做過下功課,依家大概定個行程就咁:<br />\nDay 1,2 台中<br />\nDay 3 清境-合歡山 (清境民宿)<br />\nDay 4 日月潭-集集 (集集民宿?<br />\nDay 5 忘憂森林-妖怪村 (玩唔玩到一日?<br />\nDay 6 阿里山-奮起湖 (阿里山民宿)<br />\nDay 7,8 台中<br />\n以上行程有無咩大問題?<br />\n台中市市區有咩好去處,仲有無咩地點係巴絲推薦去?<br />\n同埋租車嗰度有無咩注意?因為中間幾日都係行山路多,唔知有無咩特別要留意<br />\n唔該咁多巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十月中去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行程同你差唔多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1 早機攞車直上清境<br />\nDay 2 清境 &gt; 合歡山 &gt; 日月潭<br />\nDay 3 日月潭<br />\nDay 4 日月潭 &gt; 天空之橋 &gt; 阿里山<br />\nDay 5 阿里山 &gt; 台中<br />\nDay 6 7 台中<br />\nDay 8 早機返香港<br />\n<br />\n頭五日都係自駕<br />\n台中其中一日想去高美濕地，但又唔想租多日車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下台中市入去通常要幾耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日月潭可以玩到成日?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n純粹唔想夜晚去阿里山個程咁趕 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">早兩年試過夜晚上山，有 d 陰影</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n求詳情</blockquote><br />\n前年 5 月份同 frd 去, 由台中自駕到台東<br />\n個星期落好大雨, 我地行程好趕<br />\n最後夜晚先趕路上山 <br />\n<br />\n山上一路都好大霧, 路上又一地碎石 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一下唔覺意就碌到尖石, 之後我地成班仔冒住大雨換軚 <br />\n最後程車起碼揸左成兩個半鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩屌你好撚冒險feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我就想問今次咁多山路，租車嗰到有咩要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好睇天氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過清境上合歡山段路都幾斜+窄下，巴打你幾多個？諗住租咩車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地3個，諗緊艾維士隻日產livina/big tiida<br />\n有咩好推介?"},{"pid":"29139f493a42bca5117baf1569a45a4b048cd4a0","tid":380984,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T21:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自駕過台灣好多次<br />\n<br />\n台中清境就三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n忘憂係伏&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n唔該曬巴打咁詳盡嘅意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎忘憂同妖怪村可以skip,橫掂佢都唔太順路<br />\n巴打有無去埋阿里山?<br />\n諗緊合歡山又睇日出，阿里山又睇多次<br />\n好似為睇而睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4997820487a2e91eb66f964b5b3fc62a4c22ba25","tid":380984,"uid":38705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T21:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>租車首推艾租士focus1.5<br />\n<br />\n實冇後悔<br />\n<br />\n四人連行李都闊落，易睇位</blockquote><br />\n佢有兩隻， 1.5 (7X) 同(8X)，有咩分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abcaf385992f4cd9fed766bc366fe443e888e61","tid":380984,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T01:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>租車首推艾租士focus1.5<br />\n<br />\n實冇後悔<br />\n<br />\n四人連行李都闊落，易睇位</blockquote><br />\n佢有兩隻， 1.5 (7X) 同(8X)，有咩分別?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貴d 果隻多d 選項，例如led touch mon,倒後鏡頭，詳情要上官網睇佢個spec.<br />\n<br />\n基本版夠架喇<br />\n<br />\n我都租過livina,外型笨重d,內籠冇咁多野玩，focus 就時代感d,信我，冇揀錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc36a456f358495c26ccabf9e9b7e466acbb9f4f","tid":380984,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite