g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隔離台灣自駕post 都好多人讚focus(我總共揸過兩次）<br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n車租有 d over budget... 我都係揀返 TIIDA 算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n艾維士喎。有時有優惠<br />\n<br />\n同tiida 唔差得遠<br />\n<br />\nfocus 都係計1500車種咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2527fe4863ce8feaaaa8ffc3951124c5eb3d7f6c","tid":380984,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T23:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日月潭係台灣大伏<br />\n竟然玩3日 祝你好運<br />\n其實台中市都好多野玩 又有夜店<br />\n玩返2日差唔多</blockquote><br />\n唔值專登去，途經就ok<br />\n<br />\n自駕可以去果個乜山遊客中心停下車影下相<br />\n<br />\n而日月潭大街就買下野算<br />\n<br />\n只係去清境前既一個補給站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f057d1f75bc5bd97737ccd1b73e0d3089cdf8e","tid":380984,"uid":113205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:55:30.000Z","msg":"自駕如果巳經去過高美濕地 可以試下去 芳苑-王功燈塔 超少人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 座塔格離有條斜路仔 上左去就係 仲可以座係架車或者落一落車睇日落 唔洗行 隔離又係風力發電可以近距離接觸大風車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有漢寶濕地好似仲正 不過未去過就唔夠膽講"}]}